}} [[2019 Copa Am\u00e9rica|2019]]|| Quarter-finals || 5th || 4 || 3 || 1 || 0 || 4 || 0\n|-\n| style=\"border:3px solid red\"|{{flagicon|Argentina}} {{flagicon|Colombia}} [[2021 Copa Am\u00e9rica|2021]]||colspan=8|''Qualified''\n|- \n| {{flagicon|Ecuador}} [[2024 Copa Am\u00e9rica|2024]]||colspan=8|''Qualified''\n|-\n!Total||1 Title||22/46||117||47||22||48||135||184\n|}\n\n===FIFA Confederations Cup===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align: center;\"\n|-\n!colspan=9|[[FIFA Confederations Cup]] record\n|-\n!Year\n!Round\n!Position\n!{{Tooltip|Pld|Games played}}\n!{{Tooltip|W|Won}}\n!{{Tooltip|D|Drawn}} \n!{{Tooltip|L|Lost}}\n!{{Tooltip|GF|Goals for}}\n!{{Tooltip|GA|Goals against}}\n|-\n|{{flagicon|Saudi Arabia}} [[1992 King Fahd Cup|1992]]\n| rowspan=5 colspan=8|''Did not qualify''\n|-\n|{{flagicon|Saudi Arabia}} [[1995 King Fahd Cup|1995]]\n|-\n|{{flagicon|Saudi Arabia}} [[1997 FIFA Confederations Cup|1997]]\n|-\n|{{flagicon|Mexico}} [[1999 FIFA Confederations Cup|1999]]\n|-\n|{{flagicon|South Korea|1997}} {{flagicon|Japan}} [[2001 FIFA Confederations Cup|2001]]\n|- style=\"background:LemonChiffon;\"\n|{{flagicon|France}} [[2003 FIFA Confederations Cup|2003]]\n|'''Fourth place'''\n|'''4th'''\n|'''5'''\n|'''2'''\n|'''0'''\n|'''3'''\n|'''5'''\n|'''5'''\n|-\n|{{flagicon|Germany}} [[2005 FIFA Confederations Cup|2005]]\n| rowspan=4 colspan=8|''Did not qualify''\n|-\n|{{flagicon|South Africa}} [[2009 FIFA Confederations Cup|2009]]\n|-\n|{{flagicon|Brazil}} [[2013 FIFA Confederations Cup|2013]]\n|-\n|{{flagicon|Russia}} [[2017 FIFA Confederations Cup|2017]]\n|-\n!Total\n!Fourth place\n!1/10\n!5\n!2\n!0\n!3\n!5\n!5\n|}\n\n==All-time head-to-head record==\n{{main|Colombia national football team head to head}}\nBelow is a result summary of all matches Colombia have played against [[FIFA]] recognized teams.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://col.worldfootball.net/equipos/kolumbien-team/11/|title=Colombia - Estad\u00edsticas ante...|website=worldfootball.net}}</ref><ref>{{cite web