a}} [[1921 South American Championship|1921]]\n|-\n| {{flagicon|Brazil|1889}} [[1922 South American Championship|1922]]\n|-\n| {{flagicon|Uruguay}} [[1923 South American Championship|1923]]\n|-\n| {{flagicon|Uruguay}} [[1924 South American Championship|1924]]\n|-\n| {{flagicon|Argentina}} [[1925 South American Championship|1925]]\n|-\n| {{flagicon|Chile}} [[1926 South American Championship|1926]]\n|-\n| {{flagicon|Peru|1825}} [[1927 South American Championship|1927]]\n|-\n| {{flagicon|Argentina}} [[1929 South American Championship|1929]]\n|-\n| {{flagicon|Peru|1825}} [[1935 South American Championship|1935]]\n|-\n| {{flagicon|Argentina}} [[1937 South American Championship|1937]]\n|-\n| {{flagicon|Peru|1825}} [[1939 South American Championship|1939]]||colspan=8 rowspan=3|''Withdrew''\n|-\n| {{flagicon|Chile}} [[1941 South American Championship|1941]]\n|-\n| {{flagicon|Uruguay}} [[1942 South American Championship|1942]]\n|-\n| {{flagicon|Chile}} [[1945 South American Championship|1945]]|| Fifth place || 5th || 6 || 1 || 1 || 4 || 7 || 25\n|-\n| {{flagicon|Argentina}} [[1946 South American Championship|1946]]||colspan=8|''Withdrew''\n|-\n| {{flagicon|Ecuador}} [[1947 South American Championship|1947]]||rowspan=2|Eighth place || 8th || 7 || 0 || 2 || 5 || 2 || 19\n|-\n| {{flagicon|Brazil}} [[1949 South American Championship|1949]]|| 8th || 7 || 0 || 2 || 5 || 4 || 23\n|-\n| {{flagicon|Peru}} [[1953 South American Championship|1953]]||colspan=8 rowspan=3|''Withdrew''\n|-\n| {{flagicon|Chile}} [[1955 South American Championship|1955]]\n|-\n| {{flagicon|Uruguay}} [[1956 South American Championship|1956]]\n|-\n| {{flagicon|Peru}} [[1957 South American Championship|1957]]|| Fifth place || 5th || 6 || 2 || 0 || 4 || 10 || 25\n|-\n| {{flagicon|Argentina}} [[1959 South American Championship (Argentina)|1959]]||colspan=8 rowspan=2|''Withdrew''\n|-\n| {{flagicon|Ecuador}} [[1959 South American Championship (Ecuador)|1959]]\n|-\n| {{flagicon|Bolivia}} [[1963 South American Champio