017]]\n|-\n!Total\n!Fourth place\n!1/10\n!5\n!2\n!0\n!3\n!5\n!5\n|}\n\n==All-time head-to-head record==\n{{main|Colombia national football team head to head}}\nBelow is a result summary of all matches Colombia have played against [[FIFA]] recognized teams.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://col.worldfootball.net/equipos/kolumbien-team/11/|title=Colombia - Estad\u00edsticas ante...|website=worldfootball.net}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.fifa.com/fifa-tournaments/teams/compare.html |title=Archived copy |accessdate=2015-08-16 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160629063408/http://www.fifa.com/fifa-tournaments/teams/compare.html |archivedate=2016-06-29 }}</ref> \n\n{{updated|16 November 2019}}    \n\n{{legend2|#CCFFCC|Positive Record|border=1px solid #AAAAAA}}\n{{legend2|#FFFFCC|Neutral Record|border=1px solid #AAAAAA}}\n{{legend2|#FFDACC|Negative Record|border=1px solid #AAAAAA}}\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable collapsible collapsed\" style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 100%;\"\n|- style=\"color:black;\"\n! style=\"width:145px;\"|Opponents\n!width=30|{{Tooltip|Pld|Games played}}\n!width=30|{{Tooltip|W|Won}}\n!width=30|{{Tooltip|D|Drawn}}\n!width=30|{{Tooltip|L|Lost}}\n!width=35|{{Tooltip|GF|Goals for}}\n!width=35|{{Tooltip|GA|Goals against}}\n!width=35|{{Tooltip|GD|Goal difference}}\n!width=35|{{Tooltip|Win %|Win percentage}}\n|- style=\"background-color:#fcc\"\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{fb|Algeria}} || 1 || 0 || 0 || 1 || 0 || 3 || -3 || {{#expr:0/1*100 round 2}}%\n|- style=\"background-color:#fcc\"\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{fb|Argentina}} || 37 || 9 || 9 || 19 || 36 || 67 || -31 || {{#expr:9/37*100 round 2}}%\n|- style=\"background-color:#cfc\"\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{fb|Australia}} || 4 || 2 || 2 || 0 || 4 || 2 || +2 || {{#expr:2/4*100 round 2}}%\n|- style=\"background-color:#cfc\"\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{fb|Bahrain}} || 1 || 1 || 0 || 0 || 6 || 0 || 0 || {{#expr:1/1*100 round 2}}%\n|- style=\"background-color:#ffffbb